SendMail Project

This project is for sending a mail to multiple people.

The sendmail contains the classes SendMail, Mail and Gmail

Mail class is an abstract class
Gmail is a subclass of Mail

SendMail class contains "main" method and returnable method called "mailhost" which will return object of type mail.
The user can add different mail hosts and send his/her mail using with that host.
The "main" method calls the mailhost method and get the object of type Mail and calls the "send" method of Mail class.
In "send" method the receiver address will be stored in properties object addresses using the method "to" in which the reciever's address is read from a text file.
Then calls the "message" method in which the Subject of the mail and main content of the mail will be stored and send to the receiver.